section.our-works#works
    //- 
    .our-works__heading.text-center.p-2.p-lg-3
        h3(class='text-mid text-light-1 weight-bolder text-uppercase' key=titlePage data-lang="head3-2") our works
        p(class='text-xsmall text-light-2 first-letter width-30 mx-auto' key=titlePage data-lang="par-8") check out our featured projects, a quick showcase on work in progress and our previous work timeline.
    
    //- 
    div(class="btn-group our-works__btn-gallery d-flex justify-content-center" role="group" aria-label="gallery")
        button(class="btn btn-change btn-outline-primary mr-md-3 rounded-0 text-light-1 weight-light text-uppercase active shrink-0 grow-0" key=titlePage data-lang="btn-2" data-select="all") all works
